snippet.title: Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Saradaaga || A Family Picnic || MCM
snippet.description:
Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Saradaaga || A Family Picnic || MCM

In this new saradaga episode of Middle Class Madhu, a funny discussion starts between 1A Master and his wife Bhagyam. The discussion later turns into a serious plan when Bhagyam asks him to plan a picnic with the colony. She motivates 1A Master to be the mastermind behind the picnic plan while they portray the plan being executed by Sarada Subbarao. Finally, after convincing sarada Subba Rao, the picnic plan gets started. In surprise, Budatha invites his girlfriend Geetha to the picnic. Seeing Geetha madhu surprises him and he tries to put a fight between Geetha and Budatha, but his plan turns out to be profitable for Budatha. Everybody enjoys the places in Vizag, and Madhu, with his Naatu Guntala Gang, starts funny plans to make the picnic even more funnier. 1A master who is so excited and looking happy in the picnic was the target for Madhu and His Gang. Watch out for this fun-filled episode, Saradaga! And we promise you a 30-minute fun ride.

snippet.description:
Hello All Welcome to thyview. here is our non-spoiler review of the film Hit 2 directed by DR sailesh Kolanu.

First things first cinema choosaka naa experience cheppali ante, its engaging.decent. baane vundi.2 hours run time helped..but but but meeru usually ilanti thrillers choodaka pothe kanuka meeku khacchitham ga nacchuthundi. ala kakunda meeru naa laaga eppativo criminal minds,Mentalist, ncis, csi, castle nundi monna vacchina mind hunter, mare of eastown, Dahmer documentary daaka ilanti content consume chesunte kanuka meeda ok baane vundi and pedda thrilling ga anipinchaka poina movie end ayinappudu oka satisfaction tho theatre nundi bayataki vastharu.and meelo kontha mandhiki vunde regular questions, Hit 1 kanna bavunda ? i would say yes, this is better written ela anedi detailed ga tharuvatha cheptha.  and next question vacchesi hit2 choodali ante mundu hit1 choodala ? well choosthe konni connections artham avuthai, but choodakapoina hit2 works as a stand alone film.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Lyrics:
Dum dum damke jhumka mera, maarda lashkaara,

Rang birangi odhni main, odh aayi yaara,

Sun zara bole kya dil ka iktara..

Resham ka.. haan
Resham ka roomal gale mein daal ke,  tu aaja na.. aa wait karoon main, 

Main cherry wali lipistick lagake, arey.. kab se khadi hoon darwajje pe..

Resham ka.... haan

Meri nathani haale dole, mera bichhua chham bole, Re ,

Meri nathani haale dole, mera bichhua chham chham bole..

Meri laal chunariya, sar se sarakati jaaye

Dildaar mere main, haan branded wala perfume lagaake are, kab se chhupi hoon mai rajaayi mein, o o

Resham ka.. Haan

Jab jab dekhoon chehra tera,
Hosh huye aawaara
Bajaran teri huyi main,
Tu mera banjaara,

Dholna  sabse tu mujhko hai pyaara,

Resham ka...
Resham ka roomal gale mein daalke tu aa jaana, darling mere main,. Main mehngi waali goggle lagake yaham  kab se khadi hoon darwajje pe..oo

Resham ka...

Mai cherry wali lipistick lagake are
Mai mehengi wali goggle lagake aha
Han branded wala perfume lagake  

Kabse khadi hun darawajje pe,o o o
Resham Ka.. Haa

snippet.title: Match Highlights - Japan 2:1 Spain - FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 | JioCinema & Sports18
snippet.description:
After pulling off an incredible upset against Germany in their opening fixture, Japan pulled off another heist against a European giant by defeating Spain 2-1. With this comeback victory, Japan topped Group E, and sealed their place in #Qatar2022 - Round of 16.

Luis Enrique‚Äôs side were unbeaten in the opening two matches. They opened the scoring in the 11th minute with Alvaro Morata netting his third goal of the campaign. However, two quickfire strikes from Ritsu Doan and Ao Tanaka within three minutes of each other in the second half put the Blue Samurais in the driving seat. La Furia Roja's search for an elusive equaliser ended in vain, however, they finished second in Group E courtesy of Germany's 4-2 win over Costa Rica, thus qualifying for the knockouts.

snippet.title: Armaan Malik - Sun Maahi (Official Music Video) | Amaal Mallik, Kunaal Vermaa | Always Music Global
snippet.description:
'Sun Maahi' talks about the ethereal feeling of being completely lost in the magical world of this one's love and creating a universe of their own. It's not limited to your romantic partners but for anyone who you would go to the moon and back. The lyrics written by Kunaal will take you on the ride of exploring the enchanting journey of failing to know how and why you love someone backed with Amaal's fervent composition that gives my vocals a perfect canvas to articulate my emotions. I sincerely hope that my fans experience 'Sun Maahi' and get transported into their own world of unexplained, beautiful, and surreal love-stories.

snippet.title: WOH ‚Äì Ikka x Dino James x Badshah (Official Lyric Video) | Def Jam India
snippet.description:
India‚Äôs Hip-Hop superstars Ikka, Dino James & Badshah come together to channel their inner hopeless romanticism on ‚ÄòWoh.‚Äô The track captures the immense hurt, emotions and male vulnerability which comes at the backdrop of a heartbreak. ‚ÄòWoh‚Äô is one of the very few records which portray a man‚Äôs emotions with evocative honesty and reveals the softer side of him. Dino James pens down the difficulties behind missing someone that he has loved. He feels helpless and apologetic. Ikka feels his heart sinking as he is incapable of fixing the broken relationship and cannot deal with the heartache anymore. Badshah‚Äôs verse starts by asserting that it is okay for a man to break down and go through the gut-wrenching feeling of a fleeting romance. ‚ÄòWoh‚Äô is an extremely personal track which is bound to shake you if you have ever loved someone.

Stream Now on Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/track/1QUU43rTDMnGl4xyaIfsYN?si=42981c97ba014563

snippet.title: Match Highlights - South Korea 2:1 Portugal - FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 | JioCinema & Sports18
snippet.description:
Placed third in Group H coming into this clash, South Korea needed to grab all three points against already-qualified Portugal and hope the result of #GHAURU would be in their favour.

Ricardo Horta broke the deadlock in the opening five minutes but Kim Young-gwon helped the Asian side draw level in the 27th minute.

Paulo Bento's side kept pushing for the winner and were finally rewarded in injury time when Hwang Hee-Chan rifled home to send South Korea to the knockout stages for the first time since 2010.

snippet.title: Match Highlights - Poland 0:2 Argentina - FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 | JioCinema & Sports18
snippet.description:
A game that had major ramifications for all teams in Group C. Argentina & Poland clashed at Stadium 974, knowing a draw would take both sides through provided the other result too ends in their favour.

But nothing could be risked and that's how both sides played. Lionel Messi had a penalty saved in the first half & a tense half appeared to be on the cards. But Alexis Mac Allister with a scuffed effort put Argentina ahead & Julian Alvarez doubled the lead for the South Americans. Lionel Scaloni's side attacked at the closing minutes only for their attempt to be cleared off the line.

Despite the outcome of this high-octane clash, both Poland and Argentina marched into the #Qatar2022 Round of 16 as Mexico fell short against Saudi Arabia.

Hailing from a lower-middle-class family, Kiran is a selfish and arrogant girl who aspires to achieve a lifestyle through mending her ways and taking shortcuts. Kiran‚Äôs mother Nusrat Ara is aware of her daughter‚Äôs nature and doesn‚Äôt stop her from doing anything. On the contrary, Ujala is a well-mannered and beautiful girl who lives with Kiran‚Äôs family and strives to become independent. 

Zarbab, a handsome young man who belongs to an influential and wealthy family. His first meeting with Kiran turns out to be magical as he falls in love at first sight. Kiran sees him as a way to advance forward in life and builds a web of lies and deceit around Zarbab. On the other hand, Ujala is forced to live a life deprived of love and unfulfilled dreams.

Will Ujala ever find the love and respect that she deserves? After building her life on lies and deception, how long will Kiran be able to conceal the truth?

snippet.description:
Episode 3629: 
--------------------------------------------------------
As he can't find his scooter, "Sakharam," Bhide begins to complain. The scooter is nowhere to be found when everyone in Gokuldham starts seeking it. First, Bhide thinks Jethalal must have pulled a trick on him, but after looking into it, he realizes Jethalal had nothing to do with "Sakharam" going missing. Tapu Sena, who was Bhide's second suspect, is cleared in this case as well. Unexpectedly, Sodhi took "Sakharam" for repair after noticing it vibrating oddly. Watch the full episode to know more.

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: Match Highlights - Costa Rica 2:4 Germany - FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 | JioCinema & Sports18
snippet.description:
For the 2nd #FIFAWorldCup edition running, Germany have been knocked out in the group stage. The four-time world champions needed to win & also needed Spain to do them a favour by beating Japan.

Serge Gnabry put the Germans ahead in the 10th minute but Yeltsin Tejeda & Juan Pablo Vargas turned it around in the second half to revive Costa Rican hopes of a surprise qualification.

Germany were now left needing a massive result owing to Japan's turnaround in the other game. They went on to reclaim the lead through Kai Havertz's brace. Niclas Fullkrug got in on the act to make it 4-2 but that left Hansi Flick's side short by five goals, sending both sides out of the competition.
